-- Old Mutual Securities of Kenya Appoints Bodo as Head of Research
-- B y   E r i c   O m b o k
-- 2012-05-03T07:28:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-03/old-mutual-securities-of-kenya-appoints-bodo-as-head-of-research.html
Old Mutual Securities Ltd. of  Kenya 
appointed George Bodo as head of research.  Bodo was previously an equity strategist at Nairobi-based
Apex Africa Capital Ltd., he said in a phone interview today
from the capital city.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eric Ombok in Nairobi at 
 eombok@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
